          <p class="kicker">Case Study</p>
          <h1 class="balance no-widow">This Site v2: editorial clarity, premium controls</h1>
          <p data-site-thissite-intro>A luxury, static-first portfolio system built for speed and traceability: public pages stay frictionless while privileged admin workflows remain access-gated, role-enforced, and auditable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="this-site-stat-grid" data-site-thissite-proof-grid>
          <article class="this-site-stat-card">
            <p class="this-site-stat-value">Access-gated admin</p>
